<PRE>















































</PRE>

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=490>

<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" BGCOLOR="#cc6600">&nbsp;<A NAME="one"><FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-1" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><B>What makes a good review?</B></FONT></A></TD>

</TR>



<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">

Whether you think the place you are reviewing was fantastic, or you thought it was awful, we want to hear your opinion. You can write as much or as little as you like, but try to avoid one word reviews

<BR>

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-2"><a href="#top">top</a></FONT>

</TD></TR>

<!-- spacer -->

<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><IMG SRC="../../pix/white_1x1.gif" WIDTH=1 HEIGHT=1 HSPACE=0 VSPACE=10 BORDER=0 ALT=""></TD>

</TR>







<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" BGCOLOR="#cc6600">&nbsp;<A NAME="two"><FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-1" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><B>What you shouldn't include</B></FONT></A></TD>

</TR>

<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">

All reviews are checked before they are put on Bush Internet. You should avoid including the following things as your review may be edited, or rejected. 



<BR>



        

<UL TYPE = "circle">

        <LI>Racist, sexist or homophobic comments<BR>

        <LI>Swear words<BR>

        <LI>Telephone numbers or addresses<BR>

        <LI>Advertising or details of pricing and availability<BR>

        <LI>HTML or URLS<BR>

        <LI>Reviews written entirely in capital letters<BR>

        <LI>Anything that is time sensitive, and may become out of date.<BR>

        <LI>References to other reviews on the page<BR>

        <LI>Personal attacks<BR>

        <LI>Anything that gives away the story<BR>

        <LI>Anything that isn't your own work<BR>

        <LI>Reviews written in any language other than English

        </UL>

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-2"><a href="#top">top</a></FONT>

</TD></TR>

<!-- spacer -->

<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><IMG SRC="../../pix/white_1x1.gif" WIDTH=1 HEIGHT=1 HSPACE=0 VSPACE=10 BORDER=0 ALT=""></TD>

</TR>





<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" BGCOLOR="#cc6600">&nbsp;<A NAME="three"><FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-1" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><B>What happens once you have submitted your review?</B></FONT></A></TD>

</TR>

<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">

Once you have submitted your review a moderator will check that it conforms with our rules, and will publish it on our site. 

<BR>

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-2"><a href="#top">top</a></FONT>

</TD></TR>

<!-- spacer -->

<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><IMG SRC="../../pix/white_1x1.gif" WIDTH=1 HEIGHT=1 HSPACE=0 VSPACE=10 BORDER=0 ALT=""></TD>

</TR>





<!-- <TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" BGCOLOR="#ff9900"> <FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-1" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><B><A NAME="four">What are the rules?</B></FONT></A></TD>

</TR>

<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">

We have a number of common sense rules in place to ensure that the user reviews are suitable for all our readers. You can read the rules <A HREF="">here</A>.

<BR>

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-2"><a href="#top">top</a></FONT> 

</TD></TR>



