<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><IMG SRC="../../pix/white_1x1.gif" WIDTH=1 HEIGHT=1 HSPACE=0 VSPACE=10 BORDER=0 ALT=""></TD>

</TR> -->





<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" BGCOLOR="#cc6600">&nbsp;<A NAME="five"><FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-1" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><B>What is a moderator?</B></FONT></A></TD>

</TR>

<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">

Moderators are volunteers who help to make sure that the user reviews you see are suitable for all visitors to Bush Internet. They check all the reviews before they appear on the site and will let you know if, for any reason your post cannot be added. If you'd like to be a moderator, <A HREF="http://www.bush-internet.com/travel/resortfinder/ userreviews@london.virgin.net">send us an email</A> and we'll tell you how.

<BR>

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-2"><a href="#top">top</a></FONT>

</TD></TR>

<!-- spacer -->

<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><IMG SRC="../../pix/white_1x1.gif" WIDTH=1 HEIGHT=1 HSPACE=0 VSPACE=10 BORDER=0 ALT=""></TD>

</TR>





<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" BGCOLOR="#cc6600">&nbsp;<A NAME="six"><FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-1" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><B>Where can I go from here?</B></FONT></A></TD>

</TR>

<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">

After you've written your review, if you would like to discuss it, or any other aspect of travel with others, you can <A HREF="http://discussion.virgin.net/cgi-bin/WebX.fcgi?14@@/Travel%20discussion">join the debate in Travel Discussion</A>. 

<BR>

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-2"><a href="#top">top</a></FONT>

</TD></TR>

<!-- spacer -->

<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"><IMG SRC="../../pix/white_1x1.gif" WIDTH=1 HEIGHT=1 HSPACE=0 VSPACE=10 BORDER=0 ALT=""></TD>

</TR>



<TR>

<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" BGCOLOR="#cc6600">&nbsp;<A NAME="seven"><FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-1" COLOR="#FFFFFF"><B>Queries</B></FONT></A></TD>

</TR>

<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">If you have any questions or suggestions about user reviews, <A HREF="http://www.bush-internet.com/travel/resortfinder/userreviews@london.virgin.net">we'd love to hear from you</A>.

<BR>

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE="-2"><a href="#top">top</a></FONT>

</TD></TR>

